Question : Write an SQL query to retrieve employee details from each department who have a salary greater than the average salary in their department.


select Emp_No, Emp_Name, Job_Name, Manager_Id, salary, Department 
from Employees e1
where salary > (select avg(salary) 
                from Employees e2 
                where e1.Department = e2.Department);
